{"tid":760104,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶買水草估唔到都ok","createTime":"2018-07-29T08:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T14:00:15.000Z","uid":193077,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dc93066a1974cbdcef7620fec125655cab20a98b","tid":760104,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"本身想買下膠喉同氣閘之類嘅魚缸用品<br />\n<br />\n但見到同舖有賣埋水草，8蚊人仔一塊好似幾抵屌，買左兩塊試試運落香港o唔ok<br />\n<br />\n我用埋集運，拆包裝見到啲水草仲無穿無爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢用保鮮袋入住再用濕報紙包好<br />\n打開仲未乾哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/161922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F161922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d1a09a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲草無穿無爛，我諗未死掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/161919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F161919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=27aa3abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放左落養住<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/161911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F161911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0ad2a6b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有買水草膠，試左同人地講一樣<br />\n乾完會白色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/161909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F161909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8693be55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外買左嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/161916_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F161916_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ff275f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後影個魚缸俾大家睇睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/162455_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F162455_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5e422f21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff59117cfc7648b49623da7adb0b0e0b43229a1c","tid":760104,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"靚喎ching"},{"pid":"2f9270e7c0bea1e636bed1f40c66e53848edaaf5","tid":760104,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"樓主入埋我地水草post一齊討論啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418f73cc7b3aec425632ea9e19990c05597dac75","tid":760104,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff59117cfc7648b49623da7adb0b0e0b43229a1c","tid":760104,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"靚喎ching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"溫度高又冇水冷<br />\n啲草枯枯地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1cfdf579259c99a25dfd763059d91da65b8375","tid":760104,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9270e7c0bea1e636bed1f40c66e53848edaaf5","tid":760104,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"樓主入埋我地水草post一齊討論啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"我呢個開箱文黎<br />\n分享下<br />\n我將條link放返去果邊"},{"pid":"a30e299c13733da593924824a2dd